            <title>Thunderobot 猎刃 16 2024 电竞笔电，高效性能 + 三风扇五热管散热技术 + 16 吋 240Hz 荧幕</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/thunderobot-16-20241244491/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=thunderobot-16-20241244491</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/thunderobot-16-20241244491/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[科技潮人]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 09:30:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Thunderobot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[猎刃 16 2024]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1244491</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Thunderobot 推出全新「猎刃 16 2024 」电竞笔电，搭载最新 Intel Core i9-14900HX 处理器，NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070 笔电显示卡，16GB DDR5 RAM，1TB PCIe M.2 SSD 配置，采用 16 吋，2.5K 2560&#215;1600 解像度，240Hz 极速刷新率的 IPS 显示面板，配备全新及强劲的三风扇五热管散热技术，带来媲美桌面电脑的极速游戏体验。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864290-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293-694x418.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="418" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293-694x418.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864293.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Thunderobot 猎刃 16 2024 外观设计延续 Thunderobot 笔电的电竞风格，采用锋利的刻线元素及机能标识，搭配 Thunderobot ARGB 灯效 Logo，尽显 Thunderobot 独有的电竞魅力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cpugpu-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>搭载 Intel Core i9-14900HX 处理器及 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070 8GB GDDR6 笔电显示卡，为用家提供出色的电脑效能及 NVIDIA 最新的 RTX 40 系列的 AI 技术。通过 Thunderobot 的 Control Center 内将系统的模式切换为「独显直连」— 极致的游戏效能体验、「混合输出」— 效能与续航能力达至平衡、「核显输出」— 突出的续航能力表现。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244503" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-694x576.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="576" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-694x576.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd.jpg 1084w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-694x346.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="346" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-694x346.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ramssd-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Thunderobot 猎刃 16 2024 采用 16GB DDR5 5600MHz 记忆体及 1TB NVMe PCIe 4.0 M.2 固态硬碟，轻松满足游戏及日常办公需求。同时间都提供 2 条合共最高支援 64GB DDR5 5600MHz 的槽位及 2 条支援 M.2 固态硬碟的槽位，方便自由更换及升级储存容量。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-694x557.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="557" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-694x557.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor.jpg 1121w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244501" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2-652x580.jpg" alt="" width="652" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2-652x580.jpg 652w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor2.jpg 1011w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 652px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1-658x580.jpg" alt="" width="658" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1-658x580.jpg 658w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monitor-1.jpg 1021w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 658px" /></a></p><p>显示萤幕采用京东方的 16 吋 IPS 面板，搭配笔电的黄金 16：10 显示比例、2K 2560&#215;1600 超清解像度、240Hz 极速刷新率、100% sRGB 色域及 DC 调光功能，呈现细腻、超高清、真实及流畅的视觉体验，同时也避免长时间使用产生的眼睛疲劳。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-694x288.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="288" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-694x288.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1-648x580.jpg" alt="" width="648" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1-648x580.jpg 648w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/keyboard-1.jpg 1005w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 648px" /></a></p><p>键盘采用下沉式的全尺寸的方向键及拥有独立的数字键区，按键使用 1.8mm 超长键程、0.2T 微弧键帽、抗指纹图层表面及三分区 RGB 背光灯效，同时将电源键独立于键盘之外，避免误触的尴尬情况。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718864326-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>底部使用大面积的散热开孔，更有效的快速排走热量。内部采用全新的「飍」(三风扇五热管) 散热技术，相交于普遍的笔电散热设计采用双风扇设计，Thunderobot 猎刃 16 2024 新增「Auxiliary Cooling Fan」，打造直冲式散热模式，降低风扇噪音，提升散热及降低内部零件的温度。</p><p>凡于 2024 年 6 月 1 日至 2024 年 6 月 30 日，购买汉科代理之 Machenike / Thunderobot 迷你电脑或电竞手提电脑，即可登记换领《Elden Ring Shadow of the Erdtree》(Steam 版) DLC 乙份。</p><p>活动详情及登记表格：<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchv2vrmXijR_QKcQAI53GzbJRE5C7o-oqykK-GFgnWKWQbQg/viewform">https://bit.ly/June_Redeem</a></p><h2>Thunderobot 猎刃 16 (2024) 电竞笔电</h2><p>详情：<a href="https://shop.hornington.com/products/thunderobot-r16-2024">https://shop.hornington.com/products/thunderobot-r16-2024</a></p><p>售价：HK$11,999</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/thunderobot-16-20241244491/notebook/">Thunderobot 猎刃 16 2024 电竞笔电，高效性能 + 三风扇五热管散热技术 + 16 吋 240Hz 荧幕</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
